c: 61
v: 6
t: "And (remember) when Isa, the son of Maryam, said, “O children of Israel! I am a messenger of Allah (sent) to you, confirming that which is before me of the Torah and conveying the good news of a messenger who will come after me, his name being Ahmed (Muhammed).” But when he came to them with clear proofs, they said, “This is clear magic.”"